**Related**: Issue #[number]
```

#### 12. Best Practices

**Task Hygiene:**
- Keep tasks up-to-date
- Archive completed tasks weekly
- Break down tasks that take > 3 days
- One person per task
- Clear ownership

**Communication:**
- Update status when it changes
- Add blocker details immediately
- Link to related work
- Notify team of blockers

**Planning:**
- Break down work before starting
- Estimate effort realistically
- Identify dependencies early
- Set realistic targets

